column5: Great day today, saw some fish, missed some fish and caught this beauty on a Jackpot....great fight and back in she went. Can't wait for tomorrow..  Great start to 2011...
She even left me with a souvenir...
awesome! what did you catch it on?
A jackpot...she hit it 3 times before I got a hook into her, what a rush....
Congrats Matt nice of her to leave ya a tooth I guess each time you catch one over 48" you will be trying to match the tooth to the mouth and see if she came back
I'd bronze that tooth and make a necklace of it that would be cool Oh topwater bite awesome!
nice fish and nice reward too

Two thumbs way up on that ski...  I wasn't able to fish the Ottawa opener this year... Im hoping to get out during the week this week to see if I can get me a biggun like that... I've got 4 in my boat so far this year but nothing over 40" yet... It will happen soon tho... The st.lawrence bite should be on soon too
